\par For the Lord knoweth the way of the righteous, and the way of the ungodly shall perish. Alleluia, alleluia, alleluia.
\par 
\par Serve ye the Lord with fear, and rejoice in Him with trembling. Alleluia, alleluia, alleluia.
\par 
\par Blessed are all that have put their trust in Him. Alleluia, alleluia, alleluia.
\par 
\par Arise, O Lord, save me, O my God. Alleluia, alleluia, alleluia.
\par 
\par Salvation is of the Lord, and Thy blessing is upon Thy people. Alleluia, alleluia, alleluia.
\par 
\par Glory to the Father, and to the Son, and to the Holy Spirit. Alleluia, alleluia, alleluia.
\par 
\par Both now and ever, and unto the ages of ages. Amen. Alleluia, alleluia, alleluia.
\par 
