\par 
\par }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Chanters}{\f5\insrsid2316286 : Lord, have mercy.
\par 
\par O Lord Almighty, the God of our fathers, we pray Thee, hearken and have mercy.
\par 
\par }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Chanters}{\f5\insrsid2316286 : Lord, have mercy.
\par 
\par Have mercy on us, O God, according to Thy great mercy, we pray Thee, hearken and have mercy.
\par 
\par }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Chanters}{\f5\insrsid2316286 : Lord, have mercy.  }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Thrice}{\f5\insrsid2316286 .
\par 
\par Again we pray for the Orthodox episcopate of the persecuted Russian Church; for our lord the Very Most Reverend Metropolitan N., First Hierarch of the Russian Church Abroad; for our lord the Most Reverend (Archbishop or Bishop }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 
N., whose diocese it is}{\f5\insrsid2316286 ), and all our brethren in Christ.
\par 
\par Chanters: Lord, have mercy.  }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Thrice}{\f5\insrsid2316286 .
\par 
\par Again we pray for the suffering Russian Land and its Orthodox people both in the homeland and in the diaspora, and for their salvation.
\par 
\par Lord, have mercy.  }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Thrice}{\f5\insrsid2316286 .
\par 
\par Again we pray that He may deliver His people from the bitter torment of the godless authority, and confirm in us oneness of mind, brotherly love and piety.
\par 
\par }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Chanters}{\f5\insrsid2316286 : Lord, have mercy.  }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Thrice}{\f5\insrsid2316286 .
\par 
\par Again we pray for this land, its authorities and armed forces.
\par 
\par }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Chanters}{\f5\insrsid2316286 : Lord, have mercy.  }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Thrice}{\f5\insrsid2316286 .
\par 
\par Again we pray for the blessed and ever-memorable founders of this holy temple (}{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 if it be a monastery}{\f5\insrsid2316286 
: this holy monastery), and for all our fathers and brethren gone to their rest before us, and the Orthodox here and everywhere laid to sleep.
\par 
\par }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Chanters}{\f5\insrsid2316286 : Lord, have mercy.  }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Thrice}{\f5\insrsid2316286 .
\par 
\par Again we pray for mercy, life, peace, health, salvation, visitation, pardon, and remission of the sins of the servants of God, the brethren of this holy temple (}{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 if it be a monastery}{\f5\insrsid2316286 ): this holy monastery).

\par 
\par }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Chanters}{\f5\insrsid2316286 : Lord, have mercy.  }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Thrice}{\f5\insrsid2316286 .
\par 
\par Again we pray for them that bring offerings and do good works in this holy and all-venerable temple; for them that minister and them that chant, and for all people here present, that await of Thee great and abundant mercy.
\par 
\par }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Chanters}{\f5\insrsid2316286 : Lord, have mercy.  }{\i\f5\insrsid2316286 Thrice}{\f5\insrsid2316286 .
\par 
